reviewText: "Well Developed" is the first video in a series of hilarious comedy videos starring America's funnist up-and-coming stand up comics. Certifiable madman Howie Mandel hosts the show which includes the following spectacularly strange events: Bruce Mahler's singing checken; Judy Carter's famous dress shield escape; Philip Wellford's flaming touch final; and a quick look inside the twisted mind of Bob Saget.
